channel.title: Adding godswords to 317
channel.description:
Hello im using 317 dodian based source and im trying to add godswords (bandos godsword zammy arm and whatever ones i missed) But i dont have the codes for the godswords any ideas where to get? or can anyone give me.?
Thanks

item.title: Adding godswords to 317
item.dc:creator: @Superd00d Superd00d
item.description:
@Superd00d wrote:

Add the models into your client, then add ints in cllass8.class. Then go and type “add model ####” for each gs, and finally add the item to item.cfg
